Package deusto.safebox.common.net.packet

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    DisconnectPacket
    Packet sent by a client to notify its disconnection.
    ErrorPacket
    Packet sent to notify that some type of error has occurred.
    LogOutPacket
    Packet sent by a client to log out of the app.
    Packet
    Super class for all the packet types.
    RequestLoginPacket
    Packet containing the information to log in to the app.
    RequestRegisterPacket
    Packet containing the information to register in the app.
    RetrieveDataPacket
    Packet containing the stored items of a user.
    SaveDataPacket
    Packet sent by a client to store their items on the app server.
    SuccessfulRegisterPacket
    Packet sent as a callback to the client when they register correctly.
    SuccessfulSaveDataPacket
    Packet sent as a callback to the client to notify them that the items where stored correctly.
